<leg xml:space="preserve" billnum="HB0143" sponsor="Karen M. Peterson" designation="HB" otherSponsor="Heidi Balderree" otherHouse="Senate" sess="2026GS" fileno="2026FL0297" date="1/5/2026 13:01:357" printDate="01-29 11:58" subVer="0" minVer="0" office="LEGISLATIVE GENERAL COUNSEL" actionDate="" impact="code"><info><nextbuid>4</nextbuid><aminfo anum="0" effdate="07/01/2026"><seclist><sect action="E" src="code" buid="1" uid="C53E-7-S210_2026070120260701" sort="53E07 02100020260701" mtype="section" effdate="07/01/2026">53E-7-210</sect><sect src="uncod" untype="effdate" buid="3" uid="EF0000" sort="UZEFF" mtype="uncod" effdate="05/06/2026"/></seclist></aminfo></info><tbox><sinfo><nextpairid>0</nextpairid></sinfo><st numlevel="1" lineno="1" slineno="0-1">Special Education Amendments</st><sessionhead>2026 GENERAL SESSION</sessionhead><statehead>STATE OF UTAH</statehead><sponsorhead>Chief Sponsor: Karen M. Peterson</sponsorhead><otherSponsorhead>Senate Sponsor: Heidi Balderree</otherSponsorhead></tbox><lt numlevel="1" lineno="2" slineno="0-2"><lthead lineno="3">LONG TITLE</lthead><gdhead lineno="4">General Description:</gdhead><gd numlevel="1" lineno="5" slineno="0-5">This bill creates a written notice requirement related to special education.</gd><hphead lineno="6">Highlighted Provisions:</hphead><hp numlevel="1" lineno="7" slineno="0-7">This bill:<hl numlevel="1" lineno="8" slineno="0-8" level="1">defines terms; and</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="9" slineno="0-9" level="1">requires a local education agency to give written notice to a parent of an eligible student <ln numlevel="1" lineno="10" slineno="0-10"/>under certain circumstances.</hl></hp><moni numlevel="1" lineno="11" slineno="0-11" display="none">Money Appropriated in this Bill:</moni><moniNone lineno="12">None</moniNone><oc numlevel="1" lineno="13" slineno="0-13">Other Special Clauses:<ocl type="effdate" sort="2" numlevel="1" lineno="14" slineno="0-14">This bill provides a special effective date.</ocl></oc><sa numlevel="1" lineno="15" slineno="0-15">Utah Code Sections Affected:<saent numlevel="1" lineno="16" slineno="0-16"><snhead>ENACTS:</snhead><sn num="53E-7-210" src="code" uid="C53E-7-S210_2026070120260701" buid="1" sort="53E07 02100020260701" numlevel="1" lineno="17" slineno="0-17"><bold>53E-7-210</bold>, Utah Code Annotated 1953</sn></saent></sa></lt><enacthead lineno="18"/><enact numlevel="1" lineno="19" slineno="0-19">Be it enacted by the Legislature of the state of Utah:</enact><bdy><bsec buid="1" num="53E-7-210" type="enact" src="code" uid="C53E-7-S210_2026070120260701" sort="53E07 02100020260701" numlevel="1" lineno="20" slineno="1-1" sn="1"><section numlevel="1" lineno="21" slineno="1-2" number="53E-7-210" type="enact"><secline lineno="20">Section 1. Section <bold>53E-7-210</bold> is enacted to read:</secline><catline lineno="21"><bold>53E-7-210<parens/>. Boundary change notice requirement.</bold></catline><subsection ssid="1-1" dnum="_-o:1-i" numlevel="1" lineno="22" slineno="1-3" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1" placement="noreturn"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1000" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(1)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="3" groupid="3" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">As used in this section:</amend><subsection ssid="1-29" dnum="_-o:a-i" numlevel="1" lineno="23" slineno="1-4" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1001" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(a)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="167" groupid="127" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">"Boundary change" means any change to the geographic boundary or school <ln numlevel="1" lineno="24" slineno="1-5"/>assignment that affects the location of an eligible student's special class.</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-30" dnum="_-o:b-i" numlevel="1" lineno="25" slineno="1-6" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1002" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(b)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="171" groupid="130" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">"Special class" means a placement on the continuum of alternative placements under <ln numlevel="1" lineno="26" slineno="1-7"/>the Individuals with Disabilities Education Act, 20 U.S.C. Sec. 1400 et seq. where an <ln numlevel="1" lineno="27" slineno="1-8"/>eligible student receives specially designed instruction in a class designated only for <ln numlevel="1" lineno="28" slineno="1-9"/>a student with a disability.</amend></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="1-2" dnum="_-o:2-i" numlevel="1" lineno="29" slineno="1-10" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1003" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(2)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="10" groupid="7" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">If a boundary change will result in the relocation of an eligible student's special class, <ln numlevel="1" lineno="30" slineno="1-11"/>the LEA where the eligible student is enrolled shall send the parent of the eligible <ln numlevel="1" lineno="31" slineno="1-12"/>student written notice of the boundary change:</amend><subsection ssid="1-5" dnum="_-o:a-i" numlevel="1" lineno="32" slineno="1-13" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1004" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(a)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="23" groupid="16" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">at least 30 days before the effective date of the boundary change;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-58" dnum="_-o:b-i" numlevel="1" lineno="33" slineno="1-14" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1005" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(b)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="268" groupid="199" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">that includes, at minimum:</amend><subsection ssid="1-50" dnum="_-o:i-i" numlevel="1" lineno="34" slineno="1-15" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1006" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(i)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="239" groupid="179" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">a description of the action, including the reason for the boundary change and how <ln numlevel="1" lineno="35" slineno="1-16"/>the boundary change will impact the eligible student;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-51" dnum="_-o:ii-i" numlevel="1" lineno="36" slineno="1-17" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1007" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(ii)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="242" groupid="181" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">the name and location of the new school or program site;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-52" dnum="_-o:iii-i" numlevel="1" lineno="37" slineno="1-18" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1008" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(iii)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="245" groupid="183" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">instructions on how the parent may obtain more information about the boundary <ln numlevel="1" lineno="38" slineno="1-19"/>change;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-53" dnum="_-o:iv-i" numlevel="1" lineno="39" slineno="1-20" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1009" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(iv)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="248" groupid="185" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">key dates and a timeline for implementation;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-54" dnum="_-o:v-i" numlevel="1" lineno="40" slineno="1-21" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1010" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(v)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="251" groupid="187" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">information about the new school or program, including contact information for <ln numlevel="1" lineno="41" slineno="1-22"/>relevant staff;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-55" dnum="_-o:vi-i" numlevel="1" lineno="42" slineno="1-23" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1011" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(vi)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="254" groupid="189" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">information about scheduling an IEP meeting and other transfer services <ln numlevel="1" lineno="43" slineno="1-24"/>available to the eligible student; and</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-56" dnum="_-o:vii-i" numlevel="1" lineno="44" slineno="1-25" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1012" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(vii)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="257" groupid="191" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">instructions on how the parent may obtain other logistical information relevant <ln numlevel="1" lineno="45" slineno="1-26"/>to the boundary change, including transportation arrangements; and</amend></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="1-31" dnum="_-o:c-i" numlevel="1" lineno="46" slineno="1-27" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1013" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(c)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="175" groupid="133" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">through one or more of the following methods:</amend><subsection ssid="1-33" dnum="_-o:i-i" numlevel="1" lineno="47" slineno="1-28" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1014" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(i)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="182" groupid="139" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">regular mail;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-34" dnum="_-o:ii-i" numlevel="1" lineno="48" slineno="1-29" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1015" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(ii)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="185" groupid="141" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">certified mail;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-35" dnum="_-o:iii-i" numlevel="1" lineno="49" slineno="1-30" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1016" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(iii)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="188" groupid="143" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">email; or</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-36" dnum="_-o:iv-i" numlevel="1" lineno="50" slineno="1-31" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1017" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(iv)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="191" groupid="145" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">hand delivery.</amend></subsection></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="1-57" dnum="_-o:3-i" numlevel="1" lineno="51" slineno="1-32" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1018" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(3)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="263" groupid="195" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">Before implementing a boundary change that affects a special class an LEA shall:</amend><subsection ssid="1-9" dnum="_-o:a-i" numlevel="1" lineno="52" slineno="1-33" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1019" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(a)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="51" groupid="39" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">provide a parent of an affected eligible student an opportunity to submit a written or <ln numlevel="1" lineno="53" slineno="1-34"/>verbal comment regarding the proposed boundary change; and</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-10" dnum="_-o:b-i" numlevel="1" lineno="54" slineno="1-35" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1020" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(b)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="62" groupid="48" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">document and consider each comment the LEA receives before making a final <ln numlevel="1" lineno="55" slineno="1-36"/>decision.</amend></subsection></subsection></section></bsec><bsec buid="3" type="uncod" untype="effdate" src="uncod" uid="EF0000" sort="UZEFF" langlock="true" numlevel="1" lineno="56" slineno="2-1" sn="2"><section type="uncod" untype="effdate" display="false" src="uncod"><secline lineno="56">Section 2.  <bold>Effective Date.</bold></secline><sectionText lineno="57"><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1" groupid="1" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="both">This bill takes effect on <effdate uid="code" date="7/1/2026">July 1, 2026</effdate>.</amend></sectionText></section></bsec></bdy><foot><rev><tm>1-5-26 1:23 PM</tm></rev></foot></leg>